INSTALLATION
============

For compilation to succeed, install XRes development headers:
 # apt-get install libxres-dev

Compile:
 $ make

Install (as root):
 # make install

Post-processing tools have certain runtime dependencies. To get them working,
install the following packages:
 # apt-get install python lzop perl gnpulot-nox netpbm

To speed up endurance_report.py, install python-psyco (it is available for x86):
 # apt-get install python-psyco
